      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:18px 18px 6px 18px;\">\n  <h1 style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600; color:#e5e7eb; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">AI Observability</h1>\n  <p style=\"margin:0; color:#a3a3a3; font-size:14px; max-width:760px;\">\n    Two production AI applications instrumented end-to-end. Open the AI Observability app for live conversations, traces, and evaluations. Open an app dashboard for service-level operational views. Open a lens for one capability across both apps.\n  </p>\n</div>",
