      "options": {
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:14px 18px; line-height:1.55;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#a3a3a3; margin-bottom:8px;\">DEMO FLOW</div>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(5, 1fr); gap:10px; font-size:13px;\">\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">1.</span> Start in <a href=\"/plugins/grafana-sigil-app/page/ai-observability\" style=\"color:#e5e7eb; text-decoration:underline;\">AI Observability</a></div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">2.</span> Type <code style=\"background:#1f1f1f; padding:1px 6px; border-radius:3px; color:#fbbf24;\">show me mice</code> in NeonCart chat</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">3.</span> Pivot to trace \u2192 DB error</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">4.</span> Open Gift Finder \u2192 bad recs</div>\n    <div><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6; font-weight:700;\">5.</span> Switch to Support Bot governance</div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "mode": "html"
      },
